title: Garoto (The)
body:
A clandestine publication, of which only one issue was released, with the numbering 0 and the indication of the 5th year of publication, on October 28, 1912.

Under the same title, another clandestine and irregular publication was released, consisting of four issues, the first on September 23, 1906, and the last in January 1907.

1912: Release of the only issue of the clandestine publication The Garoto
1906: Release of the other clandestine and irregular publication The Garoto
